Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1690.5,538.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}但当时真的很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1446,571.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}谢谢你告诉我这么多小岩井先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1321.5,618)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}说起过去的我实在很惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1746,664.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}不过终于释怀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\pos(1291.5,676.5)}{\fs52.5}{\frz-6}很高兴你能这么关心我
